OL,3,CFire service tackle moorland blaze
OL,4,Cafter fireworks set off nearby
OL,6,FEmergency services are tackling a
OL,7,Flarge moor fire close after members of
OL,8,Fthe public saw fireworks being set off
OL,9,Fnearby.
OL,11,FCrews from Greater Manchester Fire and
OL,12,FRescue Service (GMFRS) were alerted to
OL,13,Freports of a blaze shortly before
OL,14,F8.45pm on Saturday 11 July close to
OL,15,FDovestone Reservoir in Greenfield,
OL,16,FGreater Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
