PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784035119
OL,3,CFire service tackle moorland blaze
OL,4,Cafter fireworks set off nearby
OL,6,FThe fire service has not yet confirmed
OL,7,Fthe cause of the fire, but videos
OL,8,Fcirculating online show groups setting
OL,9,Foff fireworks on Saturday evening,
OL,10,Fwith one causing a small fire.
OL,12,FMembers of the public have been told
OL,13,Fto avoid the area, and those living
OL,14,Fnearby have been told to keep all
OL,15,Fwindows and doors closed.
OL,17,FA GMFRS spokesperson said: "At just
OL,18,Fbefore 8.45pm this evening (Saturday
OL,19,F11 July), fire crews were called to
OL,20,Freports of a fire in open moorland
OL,21,Fnear Dovestones Reservoir, Greenfield.
OL,26,@yD@\OU
