OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784035119
OL,3,CFire service tackle moorland blaze
OL,4,Cafter fireworks set off nearby
OL,6,F"Five fire engines from Mossley,
OL,7,FStalybridge, Hyde, Bolton North,
OL,8,FLittleborough, supported by specialist
OL,9,Fwildfire units and officers, quickly
OL,10,Fattended the scene.
OL,12,F"Crews located a grass fire and used
OL,13,Fbeaters and backpack water units to
OL,14,Ftackle the blaze. Firefighters remain
OL,15,Fat the scene working to bring the fire
OL,16,Funder control and prevent further
OL,17,Fspread."
OL,19,FThe incident comes just over 24 hours
OL,20,Fafter the death of a teenage boy at
OL,21,FDovestone Reservoir.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@HO]
